WEBVTT

00:01:27.440 --> 00:01:30.960
when I did my medical training
at Harlem Hospital, but --

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:36.760
we had no idea
what lay in store for Africa.

00:01:37.600 --> 00:01:41.336
Infection rate stood at about
two percent in my early days there.

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:43.176
These would soar

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:46.576
to one out of every four adults

00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:50.040
by the time I left Harare 17 years later.

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:52.216
By the mid-1990s,

00:01:52.240 --> 00:01:56.376
I'd told hundreds of people
in the prime of life

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:58.616
that they were HIV-positive.

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:01.736
I saw colleagues and friends die,